<p>Rich Pleasure Resources may share your information in connection with any merger, sale of our assets, or a financing or acquisition of all or a portion of our business to another company. You will be notified via email and/or notice on our site of any change in ownership or users of your personal information.&nbsp;<br />We may share aggregate or anonymous information about you with advertisers, publishers, business partners, sponsors, and other third parties.&nbsp;</p>
